# Walkthrough: Surgical Navigation GPS Pipeline

## Scripts Created

| Script | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [extract_surface.py](file:///home/mi3dr/Endo-4DGS/extract_surface.py) | TSDF fusion → mesh + camera trajectory |
| [create_synthetic_organ.py](file:///home/mi3dr/Endo-4DGS/create_synthetic_organ.py) | Synthetic organ model enclosing reconstruction |
| [register_to_organ.py](file:///home/mi3dr/Endo-4DGS/register_to_organ.py) | ICP alignment of endo mesh to organ |
| [visualize_navigation.py](file:///home/mi3dr/Endo-4DGS/visualize_navigation.py) | Interactive 3D GPS visualization |

## Pipeline

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Trained Endo-4DGS Model] --> B[extract_surface.py]
    B --> C[fused_mesh.ply<br/>camera_trajectory.json]
    C --> D[create_synthetic_organ.py]
    D --> E[synthetic_organ.ply]
    C --> F[register_to_organ.py]
    E --> F
    F --> G[registered_endo_mesh.ply<br/>registered_trajectory.json]
    G --> H[visualize_navigation.py]
    E --> H
    H --> I[3D GPS View]
```

